Interface CopyableDatasetBase

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Dataset
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CopyableDataset, IterableCopyableDataset, PrioritizedCopyableDataset
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CleanableHiveDataset, ConfigBasedDataset, ConvertibleHiveDataset, DummyDataset, HiveDataset, IterableCopyableDatasetImpl, RecursiveCopyableDataset, SubsetFilesCopyableDataset, TimestampBasedCopyableDataset

    public interface CopyableDatasetBase
extends Dataset
    A common superinterface for Datasets that can be operated on by distcp. Concrete classes must implement a subinterface of this interface (CopyableDataset or IterableCopyableDataset).
